<h3> The Game of Thrones CE Club League</h3>
<table class="table table-hover">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Name</th>
      <th>Wins</th>
      <th>Score</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <% @scores.each do |name, score, wins| %>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td><%= name %></td>
        <td><%= wins %></td>
        <td><%= score %></td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  <% end %>
</table>


<%= link_to "Add New Result", games_path, :class => "btn btn-default btn-lg" %>

<br>
<br>
<div class="panel panel-default">
  <div class="panel-heading">
    <h3 class="panel-title">Notes on Scores</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="panel-body">
<ul>
  <li> All your influence in a game counts towards your score </li>
  <li> A win is worth your 5 influence plus a cheeky +1 for winning </li>
  <li> Ties don't effect this, they are the same. </li>
  <li> A "Did Not Play" is worth 3 points. Enough to prevent you falling behind, small enough to make turning up preferable! </li>
</ul>
  </div>
</div>
